title: Exception throws when exporting data from a table containing highlight/map
description: An exception is thrown when attempting to export data from the attached report.
OB: When exporting data from a table that contains a highlight rule and a map rule in the group row, an exception is thrown.
SR: To reproduce the issue: 1. Open the attached report. 2. Verify that the table contains a group, a highlight rule, and a map rule in the group row. 3. Preview the report. 4. Attempt to export the data.
